          "id": "overview",
          "label": "Kanban Overview",
          "startSec": 0,
          "endSec": 14.100000000000001,
          "text": "Kanbus is a high-level, accessible way to run Kanban directly from your repository. You get a live board and a command line workflow, while everything stays grounded in plain files your team and AI agents can both use.",
          "segments": [
            {
              "type": "pause",
